{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/basic_economics_8/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>수요의 개념을 알고 수요곡선을 알고 있다고 해도 이를 실제 현실 세계에서는 사용할 일이 많지 않다. 실용적으로 사용하기 위해서는 <strong>수요의 탄력성(elasticity of demand)</strong>을 알아야 한다. 수요의 탄력성은 수요에 영향을 주는 요인들이 변화함에 따라 해당 상품의 수요량이 얼마나 민감하게 반응하는가를 나타내는 정도를 의미한다.</p>\n<p>어떤 제품을 판매할 때, 가격에 따라 수요량이 얼마인지를 파악한다면, 판매수입을 예측할 수 있고, 이에 따른 손익분기점을 추정하여 예산계획을 수립할 수 있다. </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b38582150e19fa54e0ac8aea4a0ab00c/e7068/image1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 60.85937499999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image1\"\n        title=\"image1\"\n        src=\"/static/b38582150e19fa54e0ac8aea4a0ab00c/88218/image1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b38582150e19fa54e0ac8aea4a0ab00c/7237a/image1.jpg 148w,\n/static/b38582150e19fa54e0ac8aea4a0ab00c/0cfdf/image1.jpg 295w,\n/static/b38582150e19fa54e0ac8aea4a0ab00c/88218/image1.jpg 590w,\n/static/b38582150e19fa54e0ac8aea4a0ab00c/77d57/image1.jpg 885w,\n/static/b38582150e19fa54e0ac8aea4a0ab00c/5a917/image1.jpg 1180w,\n/static/b38582150e19fa54e0ac8aea4a0ab00c/e7068/image1.jpg 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h6 id=\"center-탄력성을-알면-예산계획을-수립할-수-있다-center\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#center-%ED%83%84%EB%A0%A5%EC%84%B1%EC%9D%84-%EC%95%8C%EB%A9%B4-%EC%98%88%EC%82%B0%EA%B3%84%ED%9A%8D%EC%9D%84-%EC%88%98%EB%A6%BD%ED%95%A0-%EC%88%98-%EC%9E%88%EB%8B%A4-center\" aria-label=\"center 탄력성을 알면 예산계획을 수립할 수 있다 center permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><center> 탄력성을 알면 예산계획을 수립할 수 있다. </center></h6>\n<h2 id=\"수요의-가격탄력성price-elasticity-of-demand\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%88%98%EC%9A%94%EC%9D%98-%EA%B0%80%EA%B2%A9%ED%83%84%EB%A0%A5%EC%84%B1price-elasticity-of-demand\" aria-label=\"수요의 가격탄력성price elasticity of demand permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>수요의 가격탄력성(Price elasticity of demand)</h2>\n<p>가격에 따라 생긴 변화가 그 상품의 수요량에 얼마만큼의 변화를 가져오는지를 나타내는 수치가 가격탄력성이다. </p>\n<p><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>ε</mi><mi>p</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\" scriptlevel=\"0\"><mfrac><mtext>수요량의 변화비율</mtext><mtext>가격의 변화비율</mtext></mfrac></mstyle><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\" scriptlevel=\"0\"><mfrac><mrow><mi>Δ</mi><mtext> </mtext><msub><mi>Q</mi><mi>d</mi></msub><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">/</mi><msub><mi>Q</mi><mi>d</mi></msub></mrow><mrow><mi>Δ</mi><mtext> </mtext><mi>P</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">/</mi><mi>P</mi></mrow></mfrac></mstyle><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\" scriptlevel=\"0\"><mfrac><mrow><mi>Δ</mi><mtext> </mtext><msub><mi>Q</mi><mi>d</mi></msub></mrow><mrow><mi>Δ</mi><mtext> </mtext><mi>P</mi></mrow></mfrac></mstyle><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\" scriptlevel=\"0\"><mfrac><mi>P</mi><msub><mi>Q</mi><mi>d</mi></msub></mfrac></mstyle></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\varepsilon_p = -\\dfrac{수요량의~변화비율}{가격의~변화비율} = -\\dfrac{\\varDelta~Q_d/Q_d}{\\varDelta~P/P} = -\\dfrac{\\varDelta~Q_d}{\\varDelta~P}\\dfrac{P}{Q_d}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.716668em;vertical-align:-0.286108em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">ε</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15139200000000003em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault mtight\">p</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.286108em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:2.04633em;vertical-align:-0.686em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">−</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mopen nulldelimiter\"></span><span class=\"mfrac